# Heartbeat HTML archive directory
#
# Populated by scripts/heartbeat.mjs once the setup wizard applies the
# archive-injection diff. Filename pattern: heartbeat-<YYYY-MM-DD>.html
#
# This directory is the orchestrator's input. The wrapper checks for today's
# file before spending API budget; absence means heartbeat did not run or did
# not archive, and the review is a no-op for the day.
#
# Existing markdown archives (data/heartbeat-*.md) remain unchanged — the
# email-review reads the HTML, not the markdown summary.
